[
  {
    "start": 0.48,
    "end": 5.44,
    "text": "Enlighten Pro. Learn faster. I speak",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 3.2,
    "end": 8.08,
    "text": "like a pro. ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 5.44,
    "end": 10.4,
    "text": " Good morning. I'd like to check in for",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 8.08,
    "end": 12.8,
    "text": "my flight to New York.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 10.4,
    "end": 15.12,
    "text": " Good morning. May I see your passport",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 12.8,
    "end": 19.119,
    "text": "and booking reference, please?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 15.12,
    "end": 20.88,
    "text": " Sure. Here's my passport and my email",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 19.119,
    "end": 23.68,
    "text": "confirmation.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 20.88,
    "end": 24.96,
    "text": " Thank you. Are you checking any bags",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 23.68,
    "end": 28.56,
    "text": "today?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 24.96,
    "end": 32.0,
    "text": " Yes, just one suitcase. Please place it",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 28.56,
    "end": 34.64,
    "text": "on the scale. Did you pack it yourself?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 32.0,
    "end": 36.16,
    "text": "Any dangerous items or lithium",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 34.64,
    "end": 39.76,
    "text": "batteries?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 36.16,
    "end": 41.2,
    "text": " I packed it myself. And no, nothing",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 39.76,
    "end": 45.04,
    "text": "dangerous.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 41.2,
    "end": 48.239,
    "text": " Perfect. Your seat is 14A, a window",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 45.04,
    "end": 51.44,
    "text": "seat. Here's your boarding pass.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 48.239,
    "end": 54.16,
    "text": " Boarding pass? What's that?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 51.44,
    "end": 56.48,
    "text": " It's a paper or a digital card that",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 54.16,
    "end": 59.92,
    "text": "shows your flight number, seat, and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 56.48,
    "end": 62.96,
    "text": "gate. You need it to board the plane.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 59.92,
    "end": 64.239,
    "text": " Ah, okay. Like a ticket for the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 62.96,
    "end": 67.84,
    "text": "airplane.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 64.239,
    "end": 70.08,
    "text": " Exactly. Boarding starts at 10:15 from",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 67.84,
    "end": 73.119,
    "text": "gate B12.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 70.08,
    "end": 74.96,
    "text": " Great. Thank you. Can I also get a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 73.119,
    "end": 78.4,
    "text": "mobile boarding pass?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 74.96,
    "end": 82.799,
    "text": " Of course. I've sent it to your email.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 78.4,
    "end": 84.96,
    "text": " Perfect. Oh, one more thing. Where can I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 82.799,
    "end": 87.759,
    "text": "find security?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 84.96,
    "end": 89.28,
    "text": " Straight ahead. Then turn left. You'll",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 87.759,
    "end": 92.159,
    "text": "see the signs.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 89.28,
    "end": 93.28,
    "text": " Got it. Thank you so much. You're very",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 92.159,
    "end": 96.32,
    "text": "helpful.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 93.28,
    "end": 99.68,
    "text": " My pleasure. Have a great flight.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 96.32,
    "end": 101.2,
    "text": " Thanks. I'm excited and a little",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 99.68,
    "end": 103.84,
    "text": "nervous.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 101.2,
    "end": 106.96,
    "text": " Don't worry, it'll be smooth. Welcome to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 103.84,
    "end": 109.28,
    "text": "your travel adventure.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 106.96,
    "end": 111.68,
    "text": "Good morning. Please place your bag on",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 109.28,
    "end": 114.88,
    "text": "the belt and take out your laptop.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 111.68,
    "end": 117.52,
    "text": " The belt? You mean this moving thing?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 114.88,
    "end": 119.28,
    "text": "Yes, exactly. It moves your bag through",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 117.52,
    "end": 120.399,
    "text": "the scanner, a machine that checks",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 119.28,
    "end": 124.0,
    "text": "what's inside.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 120.399,
    "end": 127.2,
    "text": " Oh, okay. And I take out my laptop.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 124.0,
    "end": 128.479,
    "text": " Yes. Laptops and tablets must go in a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 127.2,
    "end": 130.16,
    "text": "separate bin.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 128.479,
    "end": 132.8,
    "text": " Bin? What's that?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 130.16,
    "end": 134.64,
    "text": " It's this plastic box here. You put your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 132.8,
    "end": 137.2,
    "text": "things in it before the scanner.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 134.64,
    "end": 138.0,
    "text": " Got it. Do I need to take out my phone,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 137.2,
    "end": 140.959,
    "text": "too?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 138.0,
    "end": 143.84,
    "text": " No. Phones can stay in your bag. Please",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 140.959,
    "end": 146.16,
    "text": "remove your shoes, belt, and jacket.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 143.84,
    "end": 148.959,
    "text": "Really? Shoes, too?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 146.16,
    "end": 152.8,
    "text": " Yes, it's for safety. Everyone does it.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 148.959,
    "end": 156.48,
    "text": " Okay, no problem. Here you go. Laptop,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 152.8,
    "end": 160.0,
    "text": "belt, shoes, and jacket.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 156.48,
    "end": 163.2,
    "text": " Perfect. Now, any liquids in your bag?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 160.0,
    "end": 164.879,
    "text": " Um, just a small bottle of water.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 163.2,
    "end": 166.08,
    "text": " You'll need to throw that away before",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 164.879,
    "end": 168.72,
    "text": "the scanner.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 166.08,
    "end": 171.36,
    "text": " Oh, I can't take water.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 168.72,
    "end": 174.319,
    "text": " No, only small liquids in special",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 171.36,
    "end": 175.76,
    "text": "bottles. Don't worry, you can buy water",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 174.319,
    "end": 177.68,
    "text": "after security.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 175.76,
    "end": 180.72,
    "text": " Okay, I'll do that.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 177.68,
    "end": 181.92,
    "text": " Great. Please step through the scanner.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 180.72,
    "end": 183.04,
    "text": " Walk through.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 181.92,
    "end": 185.28,
    "text": " Am I good?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 183.04,
    "end": 188.159,
    "text": " You're all clear. That means everything",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 185.28,
    "end": 191.68,
    "text": "is fine. ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 188.159,
    "end": 194.4,
    "text": " Thank you. I was nervous for a second.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 191.68,
    "end": 197.92,
    "text": " Happens all the time. Have a nice trip.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 194.4,
    "end": 199.777,
    "text": " Thanks. You, too. Or do you stay here",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 197.92,
    "end": 200.72,
    "text": "all day?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 199.777,
    "end": 203.84,
    "text": " ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 200.72,
    "end": 206.08,
    "text": " Yes, I work here. My flights are in my",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 203.84,
    "end": 209.2,
    "text": "dreams. ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 206.08,
    "end": 212.08,
    "text": " That's funny. Okay, bye.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 209.2,
    "end": 215.68,
    "text": " Safe travels.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 212.08,
    "end": 220.64,
    "text": " Okay, I passed security. That was not so",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 215.68,
    "end": 222.72,
    "text": "bad. Now, where is my gate?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 220.64,
    "end": 225.599,
    "text": "Gate B12.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 222.72,
    "end": 229.28,
    "text": "Gate means the place where people wait",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 225.599,
    "end": 230.799,
    "text": "and board the plane, right? Yes. Gate",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 229.28,
    "end": 234.519,
    "text": "B12.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 230.799,
    "end": 234.519,
    "text": "Oh, there it is.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 235.68,
    "end": 241.439,
    "text": " Attention passengers on flight 237 to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 238.799,
    "end": 243.04,
    "text": "New York. Boarding will begin in 20",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 241.439,
    "end": 245.84,
    "text": "minutes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 243.04,
    "end": 248.84,
    "text": " Good. I have time. Maybe I'll get some",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 245.84,
    "end": 248.84,
    "text": "coffee.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 248.959,
    "end": 254.64,
    "text": "Hi. Can I have one coffee, please?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 251.92,
    "end": 257.28,
    "text": " Sure. Small, medium, or large?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 254.64,
    "end": 260.479,
    "text": " Medium, please. No sugar.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 257.28,
    "end": 263.52,
    "text": " Coming right up. That'll be $3.50.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 260.479,
    "end": 264.32,
    "text": " Here you go. Oh, wait. Can I pay by",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 263.52,
    "end": 266.639,
    "text": "card?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 264.32,
    "end": 270.24,
    "text": " Yes. Just tap your card here.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 266.639,
    "end": 273.04,
    "text": " Tap? You mean like touch it?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 270.24,
    "end": 277.12,
    "text": " Exactly. Just touch the card here.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 273.04,
    "end": 279.04,
    "text": " Oh, wow. It worked. Magic money.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 277.12,
    "end": 279.919,
    "text": " Yep. Coffee magic.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 279.04,
    "end": 283.44,
    "text": " Thank you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 279.919,
    "end": 288.56,
    "text": " You're welcome. Enjoy your flight.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 283.44,
    "end": 292.199,
    "text": " M. That smells good. Airports are busy",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 288.56,
    "end": 292.199,
    "text": "but exciting.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 294.08,
    "end": 299.759,
    "text": " Passengers for flight 237 to New York,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 297.52,
    "end": 301.28,
    "text": "please be ready for boarding in 10",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 299.759,
    "end": 305.36,
    "text": "minutes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 301.28,
    "end": 306.96,
    "text": " Okay, that's me. Excuse me. Is this the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 305.36,
    "end": 308.8,
    "text": "line for group two?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 306.96,
    "end": 309.6,
    "text": " Yes, that's right. We'll start boarding",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 308.8,
    "end": 314.16,
    "text": "soon.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 309.6,
    "end": 316.479,
    "text": " Great. Um, what does group two mean? It",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 314.16,
    "end": 318.479,
    "text": "means your boarding group. People enter",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 316.479,
    "end": 321.12,
    "text": "the plane in groups. Group one goes",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 318.479,
    "end": 325.52,
    "text": "first, then group two, and so on.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 321.12,
    "end": 327.919,
    "text": " Oh, I see. So, group two means I'm not",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 325.52,
    "end": 329.84,
    "text": "too early, not too late.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 327.919,
    "end": 332.16,
    "text": " Exactly. Perfect timing.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 329.84,
    "end": 333.199,
    "text": " Thank you. Are there any aisle seats",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 332.16,
    "end": 335.52,
    "text": "left?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 333.199,
    "end": 336.08,
    "text": " Only middle seats. Your window seat is a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 335.52,
    "end": 339.12,
    "text": "good one.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 336.08,
    "end": 339.6,
    "text": " Hm. Window seat sounds nice. I'll keep",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 339.12,
    "end": 341.52,
    "text": "it.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 339.6,
    "end": 344.479,
    "text": " Good choice. You'll see a great view",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 341.52,
    "end": 346.96,
    "text": "when we take off. Thanks. I'm excited,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 344.479,
    "end": 349.68,
    "text": "but also a little nervous.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 346.96,
    "end": 351.039,
    "text": " Don't worry. Flying is safe. Just relax",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 349.68,
    "end": 354.16,
    "text": "and enjoy the trip.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 351.039,
    "end": 355.68,
    "text": " I'll try. Oh, and thank you for",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 354.16,
    "end": 358.0,
    "text": "explaining group two.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 355.68,
    "end": 362.759,
    "text": " You're welcome. Have a wonderful flight.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 358.0,
    "end": 362.759,
    "text": " Thanks. See you at boarding time.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 363.529,
    "end": 366.24,
    "text": "",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 363.759,
    "end": 368.88,
    "text": " Now boarding passengers in group two for",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 366.24,
    "end": 373.12,
    "text": "flight 237 to New York.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 368.88,
    "end": 375.6,
    "text": " Oh, that's my group. Time to go.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 373.12,
    "end": 377.919,
    "text": "Hello. Boarding pass, please.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 375.6,
    "end": 379.44,
    "text": " Here you go. Oh, should I show my",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 377.919,
    "end": 383.12,
    "text": "passport, too?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 379.44,
    "end": 385.44,
    "text": " Yes, please. Thank you. Okay, you're all",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 383.12,
    "end": 389.039,
    "text": "set. Enjoy your flight.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 385.44,
    "end": 392.4,
    "text": " Thanks. Wow, I'm really flying today.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 389.039,
    "end": 394.72,
    "text": "Ooh, it's smaller than I thought, but",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 392.4,
    "end": 397.12,
    "text": "cozy. Hello.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 394.72,
    "end": 398.4,
    "text": " Hi there. Welcome aboard. What's your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 397.12,
    "end": 401.52,
    "text": "seat number?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 398.4,
    "end": 404.08,
    "text": " Let's see. 18A.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 401.52,
    "end": 405.199,
    "text": " Great. That's on your left near the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 404.08,
    "end": 408.88,
    "text": "window.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 405.199,
    "end": 411.6,
    "text": " Perfect. I love window seats.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 408.88,
    "end": 413.84,
    "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, please fasten your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 411.6,
    "end": 417.12,
    "text": "seat belts and switch your phones to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 413.84,
    "end": 421.039,
    "text": "airplane mode. Thank you everyone. We'll",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 417.12,
    "end": 421.759,
    "text": "take off soon. Um, airplane mode. What's",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 421.039,
    "end": 423.68,
    "text": "that?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 421.759,
    "end": 426.319,
    "text": " It means you can't use your phone",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 423.68,
    "end": 427.68,
    "text": "signal. Just go to settings and tap",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 426.319,
    "end": 433.52,
    "text": "airplane mode.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 427.68,
    "end": 436.319,
    "text": " Oh, okay. Got it. Tap's phone. Done.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 433.52,
    "end": 437.759,
    "text": "Take off. That means the plane is going",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 436.319,
    "end": 440.319,
    "text": "up, right?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 437.759,
    "end": 441.52,
    "text": " Exactly. It's the moment we leave the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 440.319,
    "end": 445.12,
    "text": "ground.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 441.52,
    "end": 447.199,
    "text": " Okay, here we go.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 445.12,
    "end": 449.84,
    "text": "If you need anything during the flight,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 447.199,
    "end": 453.44,
    "text": "just press this button above your seat.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 449.84,
    "end": 455.68,
    "text": "Oh, thank you. What does it do? It calls",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 453.44,
    "end": 459.36,
    "text": "us, the flight attendants, if you need",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 455.68,
    "end": 461.125,
    "text": "help. Great. I'll try not to press it by",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 459.36,
    "end": 461.759,
    "text": "accident.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 461.125,
    "end": 465.759,
    "text": "",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 461.759,
    "end": 468.985,
    "text": "That's okay. It happens all the time.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 465.759,
    "end": 470.639,
    "text": "Good to know.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 468.985,
    "end": 473.68,
    "text": "",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 470.639,
    "end": 477.36,
    "text": " Cabin crew, prepare for takeoff.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 473.68,
    "end": 479.599,
    "text": " Oh, wow. We're moving. Bye, airport.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 477.36,
    "end": 482.479,
    "text": " And up we go.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 479.599,
    "end": 484.319,
    "text": " Wa! Everything looks so small.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 482.479,
    "end": 488.16,
    "text": " It's beautiful, isn't it?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 484.319,
    "end": 490.24,
    "text": " Yes. Flying feels like magic.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 488.16,
    "end": 493.039,
    "text": "Welcome to the sky, Anna.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 490.24,
    "end": 494.72,
    "text": " Thank you. I think I already love",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 493.039,
    "end": 498.319,
    "text": "flying.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 494.72,
    "end": 500.72,
    "text": "Wow, the clouds look like cotton candy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 498.319,
    "end": 503.52,
    "text": "I can't believe we're flying.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 500.72,
    "end": 505.44,
    "text": " Yeah, it's beautiful. Are you traveling",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 503.52,
    "end": 508.0,
    "text": "for work or vacation?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 505.44,
    "end": 510.72,
    "text": " For work. It's my first time flying",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 508.0,
    "end": 513.12,
    "text": "abroad. I'm going to New York.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 510.72,
    "end": 514.64,
    "text": " Nice. You'll love it there. I go there",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 513.12,
    "end": 517.279,
    "text": "for business sometimes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 514.64,
    "end": 519.76,
    "text": " Oh, really? I'm a little nervous, but",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 517.279,
    "end": 522.159,
    "text": "also super excited.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 519.76,
    "end": 524.64,
    "text": " Don't worry, it'll be great. Just relax",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 522.159,
    "end": 527.839,
    "text": "and enjoy the flight.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 524.64,
    "end": 530.399,
    "text": " Hello. Would you like something to eat?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 527.839,
    "end": 533.519,
    "text": " Yes, please. What are the options?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 530.399,
    "end": 534.88,
    "text": " We have chicken with rice or pasta with",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 533.519,
    "end": 538.16,
    "text": "tomato sauce?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 534.88,
    "end": 540.64,
    "text": " H I'll take the pasta, please.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 538.16,
    "end": 544.08,
    "text": " Sure. And would you like something to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 540.64,
    "end": 547.12,
    "text": "drink? Water, juice, or soda?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 544.08,
    "end": 549.92,
    "text": " Water, please. Thank you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 547.12,
    "end": 553.2,
    "text": " Everything feels so calm now. The sound",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 549.92,
    "end": 556.0,
    "text": "of the engines is like white noise.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 553.2,
    "end": 557.519,
    "text": " Yeah, many people fall asleep. You can",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 556.0,
    "end": 560.399,
    "text": "also watch a movie.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 557.519,
    "end": 565.2,
    "text": " Oh, right. There's a screen on the seat",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 560.399,
    "end": 566.8,
    "text": "in front of me. Wow, so many movies.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 565.2,
    "end": 569.92,
    "text": " What will you watch?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 566.8,
    "end": 572.8,
    "text": " Maybe a comedy. I don't want to cry on",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 569.92,
    "end": 575.92,
    "text": "my first flight. ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 572.8,
    "end": 575.92,
    "text": " Good idea.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 576.08,
    "end": 581.44,
    "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, this is your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 578.56,
    "end": 585.839,
    "text": "captain speaking. We are now flying at",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 581.44,
    "end": 588.72,
    "text": "an altitude of 35,000 ft. The weather is",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 585.839,
    "end": 590.959,
    "text": "clear and we'll begin our descent in",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 588.72,
    "end": 593.68,
    "text": "about 15 minutes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 590.959,
    "end": 596.16,
    "text": " Descent? What does that mean?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 593.68,
    "end": 599.12,
    "text": " It means the plane will start going down",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 596.16,
    "end": 602.48,
    "text": "soon, getting closer to the airport.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 599.12,
    "end": 605.279,
    "text": " Oh, okay. So, we're almost there.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 602.48,
    "end": 608.839,
    "text": " Yep. You'll see the city soon.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 605.279,
    "end": 608.839,
    "text": " I can't wait.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 609.36,
    "end": 615.279,
    "text": " Welcome to New York, ladies and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 611.2,
    "end": 619.36,
    "text": "gentlemen. The local time is 8:45 p.m.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 615.279,
    "end": 621.68,
    "text": "and the weather is clear and nice.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 619.36,
    "end": 623.92,
    "text": "Please remain seated until the seat belt",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 621.68,
    "end": 627.68,
    "text": "sign is off.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 623.92,
    "end": 629.44,
    "text": " I did it. My first flight alone, and it",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 627.68,
    "end": 631.839,
    "text": "wasn't scary at all.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 629.44,
    "end": 632.737,
    "text": " You did great. I told you it would be",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 631.839,
    "end": 633.839,
    "text": "fine.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 632.737,
    "end": 636.32,
    "text": " ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 633.839,
    "end": 637.44,
    "text": " Yeah, you were right. Thanks for keeping",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 636.32,
    "end": 640.16,
    "text": "me calm.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 637.44,
    "end": 641.04,
    "text": " Anytime. So, what's next for you in New",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 640.16,
    "end": 643.519,
    "text": "York?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 641.04,
    "end": 646.32,
    "text": " I have a business meeting tomorrow, but",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 643.519,
    "end": 649.44,
    "text": "I'll try to do some sightseeing, too.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 646.32,
    "end": 651.519,
    "text": " Sounds fun. Enjoy it. New York is full",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 649.44,
    "end": 654.24,
    "text": "of surprises.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 651.519,
    "end": 658.24,
    "text": "Take care, Anna. Have a great trip.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 654.24,
    "end": 661.2,
    "text": " You, too, Mark. Safe travels.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 658.24,
    "end": 664.16,
    "text": " Good evening. Passport, please.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 661.2,
    "end": 666.88,
    "text": "Good evening. Here you go.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 664.16,
    "end": 669.6,
    "text": " What's the purpose of your visit?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 666.88,
    "end": 671.68,
    "text": " I'm here for a business meeting. I'll",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 669.6,
    "end": 674.16,
    "text": "stay for one week.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 671.68,
    "end": 676.88,
    "text": " And where will you be staying?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 674.16,
    "end": 679.519,
    "text": " At the Grand Midtown Hotel.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 676.88,
    "end": 681.92,
    "text": " Do you have a return ticket?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 679.519,
    "end": 685.04,
    "text": " Yes, here it is.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 681.92,
    "end": 686.079,
    "text": " Great. Enjoy your stay and welcome to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 685.04,
    "end": 688.64,
    "text": "New York.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 686.079,
    "end": 693.519,
    "text": " Thank you so much.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 688.64,
    "end": 697.92,
    "text": "H baggage claim. Oh, there. I will",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 693.519,
    "end": 702.6,
    "text": "follow the arrow. Flight 237,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 697.92,
    "end": 702.6,
    "text": "carousel 4. Perfect.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 702.64,
    "end": 711.92,
    "text": "That's not mine. Not that one either.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 707.04,
    "end": 715.68,
    "text": "Oh, there it is. Finally. I will pull my",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 711.92,
    "end": 720.959,
    "text": "suitcase off the belt and check the tag.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 715.68,
    "end": 723.519,
    "text": "Yep, that's mine. Safe and sound.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 720.959,
    "end": 726.72,
    "text": " Hey, Anna. You got your bag, too?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 723.519,
    "end": 728.88,
    "text": " Oh, hi. Yes, I was just about to leave.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 726.72,
    "end": 731.04,
    "text": " Lucky. Sometimes my luggage takes",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 728.88,
    "end": 733.839,
    "text": "forever. ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 731.04,
    "end": 734.959,
    "text": " I was getting nervous. Anyway, it was",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 733.839,
    "end": 737.44,
    "text": "nice meeting you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 734.959,
    "end": 739.519,
    "text": " Same here. Maybe we'll meet again.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 737.44,
    "end": 741.839,
    "text": "Airports make the world small.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 739.519,
    "end": 745.88,
    "text": " True. Safe travels, Mark.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 741.839,
    "end": 745.88,
    "text": " You too, Anna. Bye.",
    "textdich": ""
  }
]